name: The Warehouse (Tomilluk)
description:
Subject has been deployed in The Warehouse for asset retrieval. Follow the audio sensor for your next objective and do not go near anything making inhuman noises. Do not approach any entities in The Warehouse, no matter what they say to you.

Built for Scream Jam 2021. Best enjoyed with headphones. Download only due to lag issues in the browser.

Credits:

Programming and design: Tom Millen, Daniel Sherman.

Asset creation and design: Jasmine Hunt
